DNC Adviser Can't Answer Tucker on Transgender Science, Then DESTROYS His Own Argument   
Fox Nation : 
DNC senior adviser blasts Trump's decision to revoke Obama federal guidelines that allowed public school students to use restrooms and other facilities corresponding to their gender identity, saying that transgender kids have been left vulnerable. From the Channel
